name: 128 Classics
overview: A compilation of thirteen of Gazette's best 128 programs, including utilities, games, and applications. Titles: MetaBASIC 128, RAMDisk 128, 80-Column Disk Sector Editor, MultiSort, Block Out, Miami Ice, The Animals' Show, Cribbage, XPressCard, Sound Designer, Video Slide Show, Math Graphics, and 3-D BarGrapher.
